	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="To trigger the In-World Abductions&#xD;&#xA;1) &#xA;CTRL+SHIFT+9 (Debug book) Go to Region -&gt; Act 3 -&gt; Undercity -&gt; Bhaal Temple -&gt; In-World Abdcution 1.&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;2) CTRL+SHIFT+8 (Camp debug book) - Invite Individual -&gt; Minthara&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;3) Walk forward a bit down the stairs and you should trigger the event. Orin-as-Minthara will run towards you and start the dialog.&#xD;&#xA;4) If you want to try the other abduction location, you'll need to reload and use debug book to go to the other 3 locations." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="122" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="In certain areas in the Undercity, Orin will abduct and impersonate a target companion. Choice of target is the same as the camp abduction, but method and impersonation is not tied to the camp." />
